@startuml
title Athena JS Docs Flow (After)
skinparam backgroundColor #F3F9FF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #1B5E20
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "Developer" as Dev #B3E5FC
card "docs/index.md" as Index #FFF59D
component "getting-started.md" as GS #FFE082
component "typed-schema-registry.md" as TSR #FFF59D
component "generator-config.md" as GC #A5D6A7
component "api-reference.md" as AR #C5E1A5
component "generator-codex-handoff-prompt-pack.md" as Pack #CE93D8

node "Runtime APIs" as RuntimeAPIs #80CBC4
node "Typed Registry APIs" as Typed #B2DFDB
node "Generator APIs" as Generator #FFCC80

rectangle "Docs Navigation" as Flow #FFF9C4

Dev --> Index : starts here
Index --> GS : untyped + minimal typed migration path
GS --> AR : details -> reference
Index --> TSR : model-first and tenant context
GS --> GC : generate path and CLI usage
TSR --> Generator : consumes generated outputs
TSR --> Typed : stable type + metadata contracts
GC --> Generator : provider + output pipeline
AR --> RuntimeAPIs : exhaustive runtime contract
AR --> Typed : typed surface contract
AR --> Generator : helper exports
Pack --> Dev : optional handoff prompts

Index --> Dev : one coherent onboarding route

note right of Index
Single entrypoint reduces search overhead.
Each page has one ownership domain.
end note

note right of GC
Config discovery, placeholders, and
feature flags are centralized and deterministic.
end note

note right of TSR
Migration path:
untyped -> model-first -> generated
registry.
end note

@enduml



